title: Anti-skid mat for accessories in an automobile

claims.preamble: I claim the ornamental design for anti-skid mat for accessories in an automobile, as shown and described.

FIG. 2 is a rear view of the anti-skid mat for accessories in an automobile of FIG. 1.
FIG. 3 is a left side view of the anti-skid mat for accessories in an automobile of FIG. 1 (the right side view being identical).
FIG. 4 is a bottom view of the anti-skid mat for accessories in an automobile of FIG. 1.
FIG. 5 is a top view of the anti-skid mat for accessories in an automobile of FIG. 1.
FIG. 6 is a front view of a large anti-skid mat for accessories in an automobile.
FIG. 7 is a rear view of the anti-skid mat for accessories in an automobile of FIG. 6.
FIG. 8 is a bottom view of the anti-skid mat for accessories in an automobile of FIG. 6.
FIG. 9 is a top view of the anti-skid mat for accessories in an automobile of FIG. 6.
FIG. 10 is a left side view of the anti-skid mat for accessories in an automobile of FIG. 6; and,
